      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           cancel    "swd/mod/prg/obj/mbckgr"                         .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Cancel del modulo "mmessg"                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           cancel    "swd/mod/prg/obj/mmessg"                         .
       exe-pgm-bkg-999.
           exit.

