      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "U"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      04                   to   v-car                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      30                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "UP  "               to   v-pfk (01)             .
           move      "DOWN"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
