      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-ann-stp-100.
       acc-ann-stp-500.
           move      rr-ann-stp           to   w-det-ctl-ann-alf      .
           if        w-det-ctl-ann-num    not  numeric
                     go to acc-ann-stp-100.
